Package de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.transform.germanet

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GNConverter
    Instance of this class converts GermaNet 7.0 to LMF-format
    GNConverterTest
    Tests methods of GNConverter and the correctness of the UBY-LMF structure created by it.
    Tests are made for GermaNet 7.0 data and UBY-LMF DTD version 0.2.0.
    InterlingualIndexConverter
    This class contains methods for converting german Interlingual Index (ILI), provided in GermaNet 7.0, to SenseAxis instances.
    InterlingualIndexConverterTest
    Tests methods of InterlingualIndexConverter class.
    Tests are made for GermaNet 7.0 data and UBY-LMF DTD version 0.2.0.
    LexicalEntryGenerator
    Instance of this class offers methods for creating LexicalEntry out of GermaNet's data
    SemanticClassLabelExtractor
    This class offers methods for extraction of semantic class labels of LexUnit and Synset instances.
    SenseExampleGenerator
    This class offers methods for generating SenseExample instances from GermaNet's data.
    SenseGenerator
    This class offers methods for generating instances of Sense class from GermaNet 7.0
    SenseGeneratorTest
    Tests methods of SenseGenerator class.
    Tests are made for GermaNet 7.0 data and UBY-LMF DTD version 0.2.0.
    SubcategorizationFrameExtractor
    This class extracts subcategorization frames of GermaNet 7.0 by parising subcategorization-mapping file.
    SynsetGenerator
    Instance of this class offers methods for creating Synset instances out of GermaNet's data
    SynsetGeneratorTest
    Tests methods of SynsetGenerator class.
    Tests are made for GermaNet 7.0 data and UBY-LMF DTD version 0.2.0.
    TestSuite
    Runs all tests for germanet-gpl module: SenseGeneratorTest, SynsetGeneratorTest, InterlingualIndexConverterTest and GNConverterTest.
